00:01:44.239 --> 00:01:45.199
will be here soon.

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:46.879
We'll have them catch the culprit then.

00:01:49.080 --> 00:01:49.839
Go on.

00:01:49.959 --> 00:01:52.519
Why do rumors say Zhang Guifen killed the chief?

00:01:52.519 --> 00:01:54.919
Wasn't she brainwashed by the Heifeng Cult like you?

00:01:54.919 --> 00:01:56.639
And buried Chu Yao alive herself?

00:01:56.760 --> 00:01:57.519
No, no, that's not it.

00:01:58.360 --> 00:01:59.839
That wretched hag tricked us.

00:02:00.279 --> 00:02:01.680
She tried to save that liability.

00:02:01.720 --> 00:02:05.120
She even defied Heiye and the chief's orders.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:06.680
With that coffin...

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:07.800
