00:02:10.279 --> 00:02:11.039
You wretched hag!

00:02:11.240 --> 00:02:12.880
How dare you do this behind my back!

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:15.119
That liability defied the Heifeng Cult.

00:02:15.119 --> 00:02:16.199
She's a demon.

00:02:16.679 --> 00:02:18.199
She'll be wiped out for sure.

00:02:18.440 --> 00:02:19.479
You actually dared to go behind my back

00:02:19.720 --> 00:02:21.160
and tamper with that coffin.

00:02:21.160 --> 00:02:22.919
If Heiye finds out about this,

00:02:22.919 --> 00:02:24.600
I'll be dragged down with you!

00:02:24.839 --> 00:02:27.039
You wretched hag! You wretched hag!

00:02:28.639 --> 00:02:30.600
Yao Yao is your own daughter.

00:02:30.600 --> 00:02:31.839
Think of all these years

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:33.559
I've slaved away for you.

00:02:33.639 --> 00:02:34.600
Show some mercy.

00:02:34.960 --> 00:02:36.440
Let me dig her out.

00:02:36.440 --> 00:02:37.960
Shut up, you wretched hag!

00:02:38.520 --> 00:02:39.279
If you hadn't given birth to her,

00:02:39.279 --> 00:02:40.279
would our son have died?

00:02:40.600 --> 00:02:41.399
Ever since she was born,

00:02:41.399 --> 00:02:42.479
she's been a curse.

00:02:43.320 --> 00:02:43.960
Do you think

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:45.960
a few coins wedged in the coffin

00:02:46.119 --> 00:02:47.559
and leaving a gap will help?

00:02:47.880 --> 00:02:48.600
Buried like this,

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:49.960
in two hours at most,

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:50.960
