00:02:51.279 --> 00:02:52.279
She is the sacrifice

00:02:52.360 --> 00:02:53.759
Heiye named for the ritual.

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:55.759
Her death is certain.

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:56.960
Stop dreaming.

00:02:58.320 --> 00:02:59.559
That's all she's capable of.

00:02:59.919 --> 00:03:00.839
Leaving that gap

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:03.320
only lets that liability live two hours longer.

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:05.600
I tied up that wretched hag for two days.

00:03:05.759 --> 00:03:06.600
Once I untied her,

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:08.039
she went to dig someone up.

00:03:08.440 --> 00:03:09.199
Not long after,

00:03:09.199 --> 00:03:11.360
she came back like she'd lost her soul.

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.160
Only then did my life get back on track.

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:18.919
You're worse than an animal.

00:03:18.919 --> 00:03:20.279
No, no, please spare me, sir!

00:03:20.880 --> 00:03:22.639
I'm just trying to survive too!

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:24.039
Heiye said she's...

00:03:24.039 --> 00:03:25.039
