00:03:25.039 --> 00:03:26.160
A demon.

00:03:26.399 --> 00:03:27.839
If she stays, we'll all die.

00:03:27.839 --> 00:03:28.520
I... I...

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:29.559
I can't do anything about it.

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:32.919
The cult is just your excuse.

00:03:33.880 --> 00:03:34.759
Chu Yao.

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:35.839
Yao...

00:03:36.320 --> 00:03:37.039
means "cut short."

00:03:37.279 --> 00:03:39.399
You named your so-called liability this,

00:03:39.839 --> 00:03:41.679
showing that from her birth,

00:03:42.199 --> 00:03:43.559
you were full of hatred.

00:03:44.039 --> 00:03:45.600
You wished for her death.

00:03:52.119 --> 00:03:52.919
No one's here.

00:03:54.039 --> 00:03:55.080
He can't beat you.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:56.759
And sees us as outsiders.

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:58.440
He probably won't run far.

00:03:58.679 --> 00:04:00.720
He'll stay somewhere familiar.

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:01.839
Waiting for a chance to act.

00:04:03.520 --> 00:04:04.800
Waiting for us to leave,

00:04:05.679 --> 00:04:06.479
or...

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:11.160
